{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"8789","heading":"Storage facility loans","label":"8789 Storage facility loans","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/ch113/schV","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe date of enactment of this Act, referred to in subsec. (a), is the date of enactment of , which was approved .Pub. L. 110–246June 18, 2008","Codificationand enacted identical sections. was repealed by .Pub. L. 110–234Pub. L. 110–246Pub. L. 110–234section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","Effective DateEnactment of this section and repeal of by effective , the date of enactment of , see , set out as a note under .Pub. L. 110–234Pub. L. 110–246Pub. L. 110–234section 4 of Pub. L. 110–246section 8701 of this titleMay 22, 2008"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"In general","label":"a In general","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"As soon as practicable after the date of enactment of this Act, the Secretary shall establish a storage facility loan program to provide funds for producers of grains, oilseeds, pulse crops, hay, renewable biomass, and other storable commodities (other than sugar), as determined by the Secretary, to construct or upgrade storage and handling facilities for the commodities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Eligible producers","label":"b Eligible producers","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"has a satisfactory credit history;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"has a need for increased storage capacity; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"demonstrates an ability to repay the loan.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":"Term of loans","label":"c Term of loans","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A storage facility loan under this section shall have a maximum term of 12 years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":"Loan amount","label":"d Loan amount","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The maximum principal amount of a storage facility loan under this section shall be $500,000.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"e","heading":"Loan disbursements","label":"e Loan disbursements","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/e","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Fe","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Secretary shall provide for 1 partial disbursement of loan principal and 1 final disbursement of loan principal, as determined to be appropriate and subject to acceptable documentation, to facilitate the purchase and construction of eligible facilities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"f","heading":"Loan security","label":"f Loan security","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a lien on the real estate parcel on which the storage facility is located; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"such other security as is acceptable to the Secretary;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/2/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F2%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"agrees to increase the down payment on the storage facility by an amount determined appropriate by the Secretary; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/2/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/2","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F2%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provides other security acceptable to the Secretary; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"of adequate size and value to adequately secure the loan; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t7/s8789/f/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft7%2Fs8789%2Ff%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"not subject to any other liens or mortgages that are superior to the lien interest of the Commodity Credit Corporation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}]}
